{"abstract": "The G.E. deal \u201cwas easy for me,\u201d Stephen A. Schwarzman said in an interview, but the welter of details for his Schwarzman Scholars program required creative thinking.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/16/business/dealbook/despite-challenges-of-ge-deal-blackstones-schwarzman-kept-a-focus-on-scholar-program.html", "snippet": "The G.E. deal \u201cwas easy for me,\u201d Stephen A. Schwarzman said in an interview, but the welter of details for his Schwarzman Scholars program required creative thinking.", "lead_paragraph": "Many Blackstone executives worked grueling seven-day weeks for a month to put together last Friday\u2019s $23 billion acquisition of mortgages and office buildings from General Electric. But Blackstone\u2019s chief executive says he has been spending twice as much of his time on an entirely different project: the scholarship fund he started at a top Beijing university.", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "3", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/04/16/business/db-schwarzman-web1/db-schwarzman-web1-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 400, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2015/04/16/business/db-schwarzman-web1/db-schwarzman-web1-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 400}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/04/16/business/db-schwarzman-web1/db-schwarzman-web1-jumbo.jpg", "height": 682, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/04/16/business/db-schwarzman-web1/db-schwarzman-web1-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1066, "width": 1600, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption":